    "description": "Do you believe that Silly Humor is an Art Form?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303160/extras/616d4abc61c45287eb43183136ab021d.poster.avif?t=1730302036\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303160/extras/616d4abc61c45287eb43183136ab021d.webm?t=1730302036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303160/extras/616d4abc61c45287eb43183136ab021d.mp4?t=1730302036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Unconventional game mechanics</strong> designed to troll and surprise you, ensuring an experience filled with laughter and bewilderment;<br></li><li><strong>Strange Objects</strong> - A series of mysterious objects, which alter the environment and are integral to progressing through the game. Finding these will be key to moving forward in your journey so keep your eyes peeled;<br></li><li><strong>Soul-stirring Compositions</strong> - A rare and beautiful musical score that only graces your ears at specific locations, further heightening the emotional and atmospheric impact of the game. Can you uncover all the game’s tunes?;<br></li><li><strong>Spellbinding Atmosphere</strong> - A dark, emotional, and narrative-driven adventure with a strong female protagonist at its core, masterfully weaving together elements of comedy and horror. Get immersed and entranced in this unforgettable journey;<br></li><li><strong>Walking Story</strong> - A linear yet lore-rich journey that encourages you to dive deep into the world of Great North Shelter 2, exploring every nook and cranny to uncover its secrets. It’s an accessible experience regardless of the gamer stripes you carry.</li></ul><br>Dare to uncover the truth in <strong>Great North Shelter 2</strong> – where nature, mystery, and humor collide.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303160/extras/ed69e9d09914b29a3723bf1d9803c5a2.poster.avif?t=1730302036\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303160/extras/ed69e9d09914b29a3723bf1d9803c5a2.webm?t=1730302036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303160/extras/ed69e9d09914b29a3723bf1d9803c5a2.mp4?t=1730302036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
